Hermes May Sell About 50% of MEPC to Help Fund Buyouts, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-26T00:32:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/hermes-may-sell-about-50-of-mepc-to-help-fund-buyouts-ft-says.html
Hermes Real Estate may sell or list
the shares of about 50 percent of MEPC, the London-based
developer it bought in 2000, to help fund new development
through acquisitions, the Financial Times reported, without
attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 